      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOLLY MISS (2) has a strong winning strike-rate here with three wins and a placing from five tries. Comes off a (34.73) win last time, scoring by a nose in a NG over 600m at this track. With a clean break looks hard to beat. REAL BONNIE (5) was a convincing 29.41 winner at Gosford last start. Has the ability and can measure up again. DRINK TO THAT (1) goes very well at the course and distance with four wins and a placing from six starts. Missed the frame latest (23.96) when eighth over 400m at this track in a Grade 5. Can hit the frame with the right run. UNLEASH SHIRLEY (8) is always hard to beat when she races at this trip.",
